06-16T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港憲法保衛戰"},{"pid":"6172ae52940bbd42db0eb399048e493060337234","tid":1229780,"uid":37232,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"香港無好既政治領袖, 無得打進攻<br />\n<br />\n暫時只有打防守反擊"},{"pid":"691fd4bb2d5513dfd8835b970a8e377c14ceb47e","tid":1229780,"uid":75139,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"37b64321fc23fc076ba18ee2831344166a9b4524","tid":1229780,"uid":54381,"like":303,"dislike":3,"score":300,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"People don&rsquo;t know what they want"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"hk independence"},{"pid":"dcf115ba955e7dce51aeeab4d62dd017b288bcdc","tid":1229780,"uid":41963,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"一早講左反送中同摩連奴泊巴士冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f20779f2d675f5de3b19920b963b7396c206bd6","tid":1229780,"uid":259120,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"6831d1c4f9bd3e3f32ef2fb644cd0bb1696b6dd0","tid":1229780,"uid":33878,"like":471,"dislike":1,"score":470,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"認真覆<br />\n社會未有咁嘅氣氛<br />\n希望黎緊有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"所以想make noise<br />\n<br />\n時機其實唔算差<br />\n一來香港經濟黎緊轉差，經濟蕭條，人心思變，政府下台壓力大<br />\n二來大陸又面對同樣問題，但極權政府就只會加強控制。所以你見到呢幾年大陸咁多AI 維穩。大陸WFC, 不過黎緊對香港既控制會愈來愈大<br />\n今次逃犯過得咁急，話要趕係20號，即係G20前定，好大可能係預左同侵反面，為左抄要走佬既商家錢而趕住修例<br />\n接落黎睇怕都會唔少柯打，惹黎反彈<br />\n<br />\n正如陳雲講呢個唔止係修法問題，而係保衛香港既問題<br />\n唸左幾個鐘都只係打得出呢1999 既野，sor"},{"pid":"ccb2fdb0424e06d98e1a555360287455ab7b76ba","tid":1229780,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a725b881ac82d0e9cfc50e5118ea7921c20c73","tid":1229780,"uid":8511,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"絕大多數香港人只係想好似回歸